    "color": 7,
    "pages": [
      {
        "front": "\n      <div class=\"cover-front\" style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;padding:50px;border-radius:0 10px 10px 0;\">\n        <div class=\"cover-ornament\">&#9671; &#9671; &#9671;</div>\n        <div class=\"cover-icon\"><svg width=\"56\" height=\"56\" viewBox=\"0 0 56 56\" fill=\"none\"><rect x=\"4\" y=\"12\" width=\"48\" height=\"36\" rx=\"4\" stroke=\"#2D5A27\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" fill=\"none\"/><text x=\"28\" y=\"35\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2D5A27\" font-family=\"monospace\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">&gt;_</text><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"48\" x2=\"44\" y2=\"48\" stroke=\"#2D5A27\" stroke-width=\"1\" opacity=\"0.4\"/></svg></div>\n        <div class=\"cover-title\">24/7 OPCを始める<br>初心者向けガイド</div>\n        <div class=\"cover-subtitle\">── 2026-03-26 ──</div>\n        <div style=\"width:80px;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(to right,transparent,#2D5A27,transparent);margin:24px 0;\"></div>\n        <div class=\"cover-author\">8 chapters</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6a8a5e;margin-top:12px;letter-spacing:3px;\">fuklet</div>\n        <div class=\"cover-ornament\">&#9671; &#9671; &#9671;</div>\n      </div>\n    ",
        "back": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">ii</div>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;\">\n        <p style=\"color:#8a7a68;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:center;\">Introduction</p>\n        <div class=\"divider\" style=\"margin:10px 0;\">&#9671; &#9671; &#9671;</div>\n        <p class=\"dropcap\" style=\"color:#4a4038;font-size:14.5px;line-height:2.1;\">一人で24時間企業を運営する——なんだかSF小説みたいに聞こえるかもしれません。でも、今、これが現実になりつつあります。</p>\n        <p style=\"color:#4a4038;font-size:14.5px;line-height:2.1;\">このガイドでは、24/7 OPCを始めるための最初のステップを解説します。</p>\n      </div>\n    ",
        "leftContent": "\n      <div class=\"cover-left\" style=\"width:calc(100% + 80px);height:calc(100% + 88px);margin:-44px -40px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\">\n        <div class=\"spine-text\">24/7 OPC Getting Started</div>\n      </div>\n    "
      },
      {
        "front": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">1</div>\n      <div class=\"chapter-label\">第1章</div>\n      <div class=\"page-title\">24/7 OPCとは？</div>\n      <div class=\"divider\">&#9671; &#9671; &#9671;</div>\n      <div class=\"page-body\">\n        <p class=\"dropcap\"><strong>24/7 OPC (One Person Company)</strong> = 一人の創業者 + AIエージェント群 = 24時間365日稼働する企業</p>\n        <p>従来の「一人会社」と違い、24/7 OPCは技術的な概念です。AIエージェントが、あなたが寝ている間もビジネスを動かし続けます。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"flip-hint\">ドラッグでめくる &#10148;</div>\n    ",
        "back": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">2</div>\n      <div class=\"chapter-label\">第1章</div>\n      <div class=\"page-title\" style=\"font-size:22px;\">必要なもの</div>\n      <div class=\"divider\">&#9671;</div>\n      <div class=\"page-body\">\n        <p style=\"font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;\">技術スタック</p>\n        <div class=\"tip-box\">\n          <div class=\"tip-title\">TOOLS</div>\n          <ul>\n            <li><strong>OpenClaw</strong> — オーケストレーター（中級）</li>\n            <li><strong>Claude Code</strong> — インフラ管理（初級〜中級）</li>\n            <li><strong>VPS</strong> — 24時間稼働基盤（初級）</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;\">心構え</p>\n        <ul style=\"padding-left:18px;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">\n          <li>新しい技術を学ぶ意欲</li>\n          <li>失敗を恐れない姿勢</li>\n          <li>セキュリティ意識</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    ",
        "leftContent": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">1</div>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;opacity:0.4;\">\n        <div class=\"divider\">&#9671;</div>\n        <p style=\"text-align:center;color:#8a7a68;font-size:12px;\">24/7 OPCを始める</p>\n      </div>\n    "
      },
      {
        "front": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">3</div>\n      <div class=\"chapter-label\">第2章</div>\n      <div class=\"page-title\">VPSを用意する</div>\n      <div class=\"divider\">&#9671; &#9671; &#9671;</div>\n      <div class=\"page-body\">\n        <p class=\"dropcap\">24時間稼働には、常に動いているサーバーが必要です。</p>\n        <div class=\"tip-box\">\n          <div class=\"tip-title\">RECOMMENDED VPS</div>\n          <ul>\n            <li><strong>DigitalOcean</strong> — シンプルで初心者向け（$4/月~）</li>\n            <li><strong>Vultr</strong> — コスパが良い（$2.5/月~）</li>\n            <li><strong>Linode</strong> — 安定性が高い（$5/月~）</li>\n            <li><strong>Sevalla</strong> — PaaS管理不要（$5/月~）</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"flip-hint\">ドラッグでめくる &#10148;</div>\n    ",
        "back": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">4</div>\n      <div class=\"chapter-label\">第2章</div>\n      <div class=\"page-title\" style=\"font-size:20px;\">最低要件</div>\n      <div class=\"divider\">&#9671;</div>\n      <div class=\"page-body\">\n        <div class=\"code-block\">\n          <div class=\"code-label\">SPEC</div>\n          <span class=\"comment\"># 最低要件</span><br>\n          <span class=\"property\">CPU</span>: <span class=\"string\">1コア</span><br>\n          <span class=\"property\">Memory</span>: <span class=\"string\">1GB</span><br>\n          <span class=\"property\">Storage</span>: <span class=\"string\">25GB</span><br>\n          <span class=\"property\">OS</span>: <span class=\"string\">Ubuntu 22.04</span>\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"margin-top:18px;font-size:13px;color:#8a7a68;\">これ以上のスペックがあれば、より快適に運用できます。</p>\n      </div>\n    ",
        "leftContent": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">2</div>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;opacity:0.4;\">\n        <div class=\"divider\">&#9671;</div>\n        <p style=\"text-align:center;color:#8a7a68;font-size:12px;\">必要なもの</p>\n      </div>\n    "
      },
      {
        "front": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">5</div>\n      <div class=\"chapter-label\">第3章</div>\n      <div class=\"page-title\">OpenClawをインストール</div>\n      <div class=\"divider\">&#9671; &#9671; &#9671;</div>\n      <div class=\"page-body\">\n        <div class=\"code-block\">\n          <div class=\"code-label\">bash</div>\n          <span class=\"comment\"># サーバーに接続</span><br>\n          <span class=\"keyword\">ssh</span> root@your-server-ip<br><br>\n          <span class=\"comment\"># 依存関係をインストール</span><br>\n          apt update && apt install -y nodejs npm git<br><br>\n          <span class=\"comment\"># リポジトリをクローン</span><br>\n          <span class=\"keyword\">git</span> clone https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw.git<br>\n          <span class=\"keyword\">cd</span> openclaw<br><br>\n          <span class=\"comment\"># 依存関係をインストール</span><br>\n          npm install\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"flip-hint\">ドラッグでめくる &#10148;</div>\n    ",
        "back": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">6</div>\n      <div class=\"chapter-label\">第3章</div>\n      <div class=\"page-title\" style=\"font-size:20px;\">.envファイルの設定</div>\n      <div class=\"divider\">&#9671;</div>\n      <div class=\"page-body\">\n        <div class=\"code-block\">\n          <div class=\"code-label\">env</div>\n          <span class=\"comment\"># Telegram Bot</span><br>\n          <span class=\"property\">TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN</span>=<span class=\"string\">your-bot-token</span><br><br>\n          <span class=\"comment\"># AI Provider</span><br>\n          <span class=\"property\">OPENAI_API_KEY</span>=<span class=\"string\">your-openai-key</span><br>\n          <span class=\"comment\"># または</span><br>\n          <span class=\"property\">ANTHROPIC_API_KEY</span>=<span class=\"string\">your-anthropic-key</span><br><br>\n          <span class=\"comment\"># データベース（オプション）</span><br>\n          <span class=\"property\">DATABASE_URL</span>=<span class=\"string\">postgresql://localhost:5432/openclaw</span>\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"margin-top:14px;font-size:13px;color:#8a7a68;\"><code>cp .env.example .env</code> でテンプレートをコピーして編集。</p>\n      </div>\n    ",
        "leftContent": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">4</div>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;opacity:0.4;\">\n        <div class=\"divider\">&#9671;</div>\n        <p style=\"text-align:center;color:#8a7a68;font-size:12px;\">VPSを用意する</p>\n      </div>\n    "
      },
      {
        "front": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">7</div>\n      <div class=\"chapter-label\">第4章</div>\n      <div class=\"page-title\">Telegram Botを作成</div>\n      <div class=\"divider\">&#9671; &#9671; &#9671;</div>\n      <div class=\"page-body\">\n        <div class=\"tip-box\">\n          <div class=\"tip-title\">STEPS</div>\n          <ul>\n            <li>Telegramで <code>@BotFather</code> を検索</li>\n            <li><code>/newbot</code> を送信</li>\n            <li>ボット名を入力</li>\n            <li>トークンをコピーして <code>.env</code> に貼り付け</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"margin-top:16px;font-size:13px;color:#8a7a68;\">Telegram Botは、あなたとAIエージェントのインターフェースになります。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"flip-hint\">ドラッグでめくる &#10148;</div>\n    ",
        "back": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">8</div>\n      <div class=\"chapter-label\">第5章</div>\n      <div class=\"page-title\" style=\"font-size:22px;\">OpenClawを起動</div>\n      <div class=\"divider\">&#9671; &#9671; &#9671;</div>\n      <div class=\"page-body\">\n        <div class=\"code-block\">\n          <div class=\"code-label\">bash</div>\n          <span class=\"comment\"># 開発モードで起動</span><br>\n          npm run start:telegram<br><br>\n          <span class=\"comment\"># 本番モード（PM2を使用）</span><br>\n          npm install -g pm2<br>\n          pm2 start npm --name <span class=\"string\">\"openclaw\"</span> -- run start:telegram<br>\n          pm2 save<br>\n          pm2 startup\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"margin-top:14px;font-size:13px;color:#8a7a68;\">PM2はプロセスマネージャー。サーバー再起動後も自動的にOpenClawが起動します。</p>\n      </div>\n    ",
        "leftContent": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">6</div>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;opacity:0.4;\">\n        <div class=\"divider\">&#9671;</div>\n        <p style=\"text-align:center;color:#8a7a68;font-size:12px;\">OpenClawをインストール</p>\n      </div>\n    "
      },
      {
        "front": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">9</div>\n      <div class=\"chapter-label\">第6章</div>\n      <div class=\"page-title\">Claude Codeを設定</div>\n      <div class=\"divider\">&#9671; &#9671; &#9671;</div>\n      <div class=\"page-body\">\n        <p>ローカル環境でClaude Codeを設定:</p>\n        <div class=\"code-block\">\n          <div class=\"code-label\">bash</div>\n          <span class=\"comment\"># インストール</span><br>\n          npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code<br><br>\n          <span class=\"comment\"># APIキーを設定</span><br>\n          claude-code config set apiKey<br><br>\n          <span class=\"comment\"># プロジェクトでCLAUDE.mdを作成</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"flip-hint\">ドラッグでめくる &#10148;</div>\n    ",
        "back": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">10</div>\n      <div class=\"chapter-label\">第6章</div>\n      <div class=\"page-title\" style=\"font-size:20px;\">CLAUDE.mdの例</div>\n      <div class=\"divider\">&#9671;</div>\n      <div class=\"page-body\">\n        <div class=\"code-block\" style=\"font-size:11.5px;\">\n          <div class=\"code-label\">markdown</div>\n          <span class=\"comment\"># CLAUDE.md</span><br><br>\n          <span class=\"keyword\">## プロジェクト概要</span><br>\n          個人プロジェクトで24/7 OPCを実験中。<br><br>\n          <span class=\"keyword\">## 技術スタック</span><br>\n          - OpenClaw: オーケストレーター<br>\n          - Claude Code: 開発支援<br><br>\n          <span class=\"keyword\">## 開発コマンド</span><br>\n          - OpenClaw起動: <span class=\"string\">npm run start:telegram</span><br>\n          - ログ確認: <span class=\"string\">pm2 logs openclaw</span><br><br>\n          <span class=\"keyword\">## ルール</span><br>\n          - 本番データでテストしない<br>\n          - APIキーをコミットしない\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    ",
        "leftContent": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">8</div>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;opacity:0.4;\">\n        <div class=\"divider\">&#9671;</div>\n        <p style=\"text-align:center;color:#8a7a68;font-size:12px;\">OpenClawを起動</p>\n      </div>\n    "
      },
      {
        "front": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">11</div>\n      <div class=\"chapter-label\">第7章</div>\n      <div class=\"page-title\">自動化を設計</div>\n      <div class=\"divider\">&#9671; &#9671; &#9671;</div>\n      <div class=\"page-body\">\n        <p class=\"dropcap\">最初は小さな自動化から始めましょう。</p>\n        <div class=\"tip-box\">\n          <div class=\"tip-title\">FIRST AUTOMATION TASKS</div>\n          <ul>\n            <li><strong>メールチェック</strong>: 毎朝サマリーを送信</li>\n            <li><strong>ファイル整理</strong>: 定期的なクリーンアップ</li>\n            <li><strong>レポート生成</strong>: 週次レポートの作成</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"font-weight:700;margin-top:16px;\">設計のポイント</p>\n        <ul style=\"padding-left:18px;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">\n          <li>小さく始める</li>\n          <li>人間の承認を含める</li>\n          <li>ログを残す</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"flip-hint\">ドラッグでめくる &#10148;</div>\n    ",
        "back": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">12</div>\n      <div class=\"chapter-label\">第7章</div>\n      <div class=\"page-title\" style=\"font-size:20px;\">セキュリティの基本</div>\n      <div class=\"divider\">&#9671;</div>\n      <div class=\"page-body\">\n        <div class=\"comparison\">\n          <div class=\"col bad\">\n            <div class=\"col-label\">&#10007; やってはいけないこと</div>\n            <p>APIキーをコードにハードコード</p>\n            <p>rootユーザーで実行</p>\n            <p>ファイアウォールなしで公開</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"col good\">\n            <div class=\"col-label\">&#10003; やるべきこと</div>\n            <p>環境変数で機密情報を管理</p>\n            <p>専用ユーザーを作成</p>\n            <p>UFWでファイアウォールを設定</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"code-block\" style=\"font-size:11.5px;\">\n          <span class=\"comment\"># ファイアウォール設定</span><br>\n          ufw allow ssh<br>\n          ufw allow 80<br>\n          ufw allow 443<br>\n          ufw enable\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    ",
        "leftContent": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">10</div>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;opacity:0.4;\">\n        <div class=\"divider\">&#9671;</div>\n        <p style=\"text-align:center;color:#8a7a68;font-size:12px;\">Claude Codeを設定</p>\n      </div>\n    "
      },
      {
        "front": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">13</div>\n      <div class=\"chapter-label\">第8章</div>\n      <div class=\"page-title\">トラブルシューティング</div>\n      <div class=\"divider\">&#9671; &#9671; &#9671;</div>\n      <div class=\"page-body\">\n        <p style=\"font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;\">OpenClawが起動しない</p>\n        <div class=\"code-block\" style=\"font-size:11.5px;\">\n          <span class=\"comment\"># ログを確認</span><br>\n          pm2 logs openclaw<br><br>\n          <span class=\"comment\"># 依存関係を再インストール</span><br>\n          rm -rf node_modules && npm install\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"font-weight:700;margin-top:14px;margin-bottom:8px;\">Telegramが応答しない</p>\n        <div class=\"code-block\" style=\"font-size:11.5px;\">\n          <span class=\"comment\"># ボットトークンを確認</span><br>\n          curl https://api.telegram.org/botTOKEN/getMe<br><br>\n          <span class=\"comment\"># Webhookをクリア</span><br>\n          curl https://api.telegram.org/botTOKEN/deleteWebhook\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"flip-hint\">ドラッグでめくる &#10148;</div>\n    ",
        "back": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">14</div>\n      <div class=\"chapter-label\">NEXT STEPS</div>\n      <div class=\"page-title\" style=\"font-size:22px;\">次のステップ</div>\n      <div class=\"divider\">&#9671; &#9671; &#9671;</div>\n      <div class=\"page-body\">\n        <div class=\"tip-box\">\n          <div class=\"tip-title\">ROADMAP</div>\n          <ul>\n            <li><strong>スキルを追加</strong>: OpenClawのコミュニティスキルを活用</li>\n            <li><strong>Claude Codeとの連携</strong>: openclaw-claude-code-skillを導入</li>\n            <li><strong>監視の追加</strong>: エラー通知を設定</li>\n            <li><strong>バックアップ</strong>: 定期的なバックアップを自動化</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"quote\">\n          最初は小さく始めて、徐々に自動化の範囲を広げていくのがコツです。\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:24px;\">\n          <span class=\"tag\">OPC</span>\n          <span class=\"tag\">AI</span>\n          <span class=\"tag\">Automation</span>\n          <span class=\"tag\">Beginner</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    ",
        "leftContent": "\n      <div class=\"page-number\">12</div>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;opacity:0.4;\">\n        <div class=\"divider\">&#9671;</div>\n        <p style=\"text-align:center;color:#8a7a68;font-size:12px;\">自動化を設計</p>\n      </div>\n    "
      }
    ]
  }
]